Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.rgp

Contains replacement command, replacement response and command extension classes for the Registry Grace Period extension.

Class Summary
DomainInfoRgpResponseExtension Extension for the EPP Domain Info response, representing the RGP Info aspect of the Registry Grace Period extension.
DomainRestoreReportCommand Representation of the EPP Domain Update command with the Domain Restore Report aspect of the Registry Grace Period extension.
DomainRestoreRequestCommand Representation of the EPP Domain Update command with the Domain Restore aspect of the Registry Grace Period extension.
DomainRestoreResponse Representation of the EPP Domain Update response with the Redemption Status aspect of the Registry Grace Period extension.
